note bottom of Readme
The README should route.
It should not try to explain every lane itself.
end note

note bottom of Empirical
Empirical data is visible and useful,
but it is not the theorem source of truth.
end note

note bottom of UnifiedOwner
The theorem-owner milestone is closed.
The scientific roadmap is still open beyond this owner layer.
end note

note bottom of TruthOpen
If a viewer remembers one rule:
do not promote red gates by prose.
Only a named theorem owner can move a gate out of this box.
end note

